name: Mike Kehoe
tweet: .@ClaudiaLKehoe & I are praying for the families of Lane Burns & Garrett Worley, & their fellow officers in the Bonne Terre Police Department. Officer Burns was killed, & Corporal Worley is in critical condition, after a shooting this morning. Our prayers are with the community.

name: Mike Kehoe
tweet: Joplin Police Officer Jake Reed tragically lost his life last week in the line of duty.
